@d2 1
a2 6
MPD is configured to listen on localhost only. To start MPD at boot time,
add the following to /etc/rc.local:

if [ -x ${PREFIX}/sbin/mpd ]; then
        echo -n ' mpd';       ${PREFIX}/sbin/mpd
fi
